title: A classic never gets old.
review: Just watched it again after many years, and it's timeless. The story, the cast, the direction, and that musical score. Absolutely perfect!

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker
title: I absolutely loved this movie
review: So I will keep this short and no spoilers. The movie was excellent. It had a good story. Very emotional. Definitely the best of the new trilogy. I liked all 3, but I liked 7 and 9 the best. All the people around me in the theater seemed to really like it too. Can't wait for the next saga. Keep them coming Disney.
